---
import { LIVE_URL } from './config';
---

<section class="faq container" id="faq">
  <div class="head">
    <span class="kicker">// Good to know</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Frequently asked</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="list">
    <details open>
      <summary>Is Choke free?<span class="plus">+</span></summary>
      <p>
        Yes. Choke is completely free and open source under the GPL-3.0 license. There's no paid
        tier, no ads and no account.
      </p>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>How do spectators watch the results?<span class="plus">+</span></summary>
      <p>
        Every match you score is published live to{' '}
        <a class="gold-link" href={LIVE_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener">bjjscore.live</a>. Share
        the public key (npub) from your Account tab, and anyone can follow your matches there —
        great for projecting at a venue.
      </p>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Do I need to create an account?<span class="plus">+</span></summary>
      <p>
        No. When you install the app a secure keypair is generated on your device. That key is your
        identity — back it up and keep the private part (nsec) secret.
      </p>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Can a helper score matches for me?<span class="plus">+</span></summary>
      <p>
        Yes. You can delegate a single match to a teammate using an ephemeral match key, so multiple
        people can run the scoring table without ever sharing your private key.
      </p>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Which platforms are supported?<span class="plus">+</span></summary>
      <p>
        Choke is available for Android on Google Play, with iOS in the works. It's built with
        Flutter, so the same experience runs everywhere.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    max-width: 900px;
    padding-top: 96px;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .head {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 44px;
  }

  .list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  details {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
  }

  summary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    list-style: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .plus {
    color: var(--green);
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  details[open] .plus {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  details p {
    font-size: 15.5px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 14px;
  }

  .gold-link {
    color: var(--gold);
  }
</style>
